tch notification being sent. If you request a cancellation in this 7 hour window and your item has already been dispatched you can refuse to accept the package from the courier and it will be returned directly to us at no extra cost or inconvenience to yourself, this only applies to UK residents.&nbsp;<br><br>If your goods were dispatched before you cancelled the order then you must send the goods back to us at your own cost and risk in the original packaging and condition. Our returns address is:<br><strong>Returns@ <br>Baby Kooky Ltd</strong><br>Unit 4D the green<br>Green Street<br>Macclesfield<br>SK10 1JH<br><br>Please pack the items so that they will not be damaged in transit. Include a copy of the packing note included in the package we sent to you and a brief note of the reason for return.<br><br><br></p><p><br /></p>
